{"query": "Hi, I'm evaluating AttendanceBot for a large customer service team.\n\nIn cases where the customer insists on something outside of policy (like requesting an exception), can the bot adapt its response or is it always stuck with a script?", "retrieved_contexts": ["AttendanceBot Plans and Features", "How can I get help from AttendanceBot support?", "API Documentation"], "generated_answer": "AttendanceBot is designed to automate and streamline attendance management, but it doesn't have the capability to adapt its responses dynamically to individual requests outside of established policies. It operates based on predefined rules and scripts. If you need to handle exceptions or requests outside of policy, it would require manual intervention or setting up specific custom rules within the system.\n\nFor more detailed information on features and customization, you might want to look into the plans and features documentation or contact support for assistance.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000138965", "reference_answer": "AttendanceBot is designed to automate attendance management based on predefined rules and scripts. It cannot adapt responses dynamically for exceptions outside of policy, which would require manual intervention or custom rules. For more details, check the plans and features documentation or contact support.", "quality_score": 4.8, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "Hi, I'm evaluating AttendanceBot for a large customer service team.\n\nIn cases where the customer insists on something outside of policy (like requesting an exception), can the bot adapt its response or is it always stuck with a script?", "retrieved_contexts": ["AttendanceBot Plans and Features", "How can I get help from AttendanceBot support?", "API Documentation"], "generated_answer": "AttendanceBot is designed to automate and streamline attendance and leave management, but it doesn't have the capability to autonomously adapt its responses to exceptions outside of predefined policies. For handling exceptions or special requests, it would typically require manual intervention or adjustments by an administrator or manager. If you need more specific customization or have further questions, consider reaching out to support.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000138965", "reference_answer": "AttendanceBot is designed to automate attendance and leave management, but it cannot adapt responses for exceptions outside of predefined policies. Such cases typically require manual intervention. For further assistance, please reach out to support.", "quality_score": 4.8, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "Can you help me fix an issue with attendance sync? It\u2019s not showing correct hours.", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to send hours to Gusto for payroll", "How to view my shifts and the shifts of my employees", "How do I find my missing employee profile on the dashboard? (Slack)"], "generated_answer": "To address issues with attendance sync not showing correct hours, follow these steps:\n\n1. Ensure that your AttendanceBot is correctly integrated with your payroll system, such as Gusto.\n2. Verify that employees are properly mapped between AttendanceBot and Gusto.\n3. Go to the Payroll tab in AttendanceBot and ensure the correct pay period is selected.\n4. Click \u201cSync\u201d to send the hours to Gusto. If there are discrepancies, use \"Re-import data from Gusto\" to fetch updated information.\n5. If the issue persists, consider re-syncing employees or contacting support for further assistance.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000112898", "reference_answer": "To fix attendance sync issues, ensure AttendanceBot is integrated with Gusto, verify employee mapping, select the correct pay period, sync hours, and re-import data if needed. For persistent issues, re-sync employees or contact support.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "What are the common causes for incorrect attendance sync? I just need a quick checklist.", "retrieved_contexts": ["How do I find my missing employee profile on the dashboard? (Slack)", "What can a manager do in AttendanceBot?", "How do I learn more about the product?"], "generated_answer": "I don't have enough information on the common causes for incorrect attendance sync. Please consider opening a support ticket by typing 'ticket'.", "reference_answer": "Common causes for incorrect attendance sync may include: 1) Incorrect employee profiles, 2) Time zone mismatches, 3) Integration issues with other tools, 4) Manual entry errors. For further assistance, please open a support ticket.", "quality_score": 2.4, "bucket": "partial"}
