{"query": "HOW DO I ADD MY TIMEOFF", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to configure overtime and time off in lieu (TOIL) rules?", "How to configure and use time-off-in-lieu (TOIL) (Slack)", "How to configure overtime and time off in lieu (TOIL) rules?"], "generated_answer": "To add your time off in AttendanceBot on Slack, follow these steps:\n\n1. Open Slack and go to the channel where AttendanceBot is installed.\n2. Type \"apply\" and press Enter.\n3. Select the type of leave you want to apply for (e.g., vacation, sick leave).\n4. Enter the duration and any other required details.\n5. Submit your request.\n\nIf you need further assistance, please provide more specific details about your request.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000112422", "reference_answer": "To add your time off in AttendanceBot on Slack, follow these steps: 1. Open Slack and go to the channel where AttendanceBot is installed. 2. Type 'apply' and press Enter. 3. Select the type of leave you want to apply for (e.g., vacation, sick leave). 4. Enter the duration and any other required details. 5. Submit your request. If you need further assistance, please provide more specific details about your request.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
