{"query": "Which services can I integrate my vacation calendar with?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to integrate calendars", "How to use and configure the AttendanceBot vacation calendar", "How to use and configure the AttendanceBot vacation calendar"], "generated_answer": "You can integrate your vacation calendar with Google Calendar, Apple Calendar, Office 365, and Outlook.com. \n\n1. Type \"cal\" as a direct message (DM) in Slack.\n2. Choose the calendar you want to sync with by clicking on \"Enable\".\n3. For Apple Calendar, use \u2318-Option-S or select \u201cNew Calendar Subscription\u201d from the \u201cFile\u201d menu, paste the URL, and click \u201cSubscribe\u201d.\n4. For Office 365/Outlook 365, sign in, click on \u201cOther Calendars\u201d, choose \u201cOpen Calendar\u201d, enter the URL into \u201cInternet Calendar\u201d, and click \u201cOpen\u201d.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000116056", "reference_answer": "You can integrate your vacation calendar with Google Calendar, Apple Calendar, Office 365, and Outlook.com. For setup instructions, refer to the relevant sections in the AttendanceBot documentation.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
