{"query": "for 100+ employees, what can you recommend?", "retrieved_contexts": ["AttendanceBot Plans and Features", "How to configure hybrid work policies", "Work Model - Hybrid or Fully Remote"], "generated_answer": "For managing 100+ employees, the Premium Plan of AttendanceBot is recommended. It includes features such as:\n\n1. A dedicated Customer Success Manager for personalized support.\n2. Priority support for timely issue resolution.\n3. Advanced features like Time-off-in-Lieu, probation, and employee-specific rules.\n4. Comprehensive project management and shift rostering.\n5. Advanced and scheduled reports for detailed insights.\n\nThis plan is ideal for larger teams needing robust support and advanced features.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000138965", "reference_answer": "For managing 100+ employees, the Premium Plan of AttendanceBot is recommended. It includes features such as a dedicated Customer Success Manager, priority support, advanced features like Time-off-in-Lieu, probation, and employee-specific rules, comprehensive project management, shift rostering, and advanced reports for detailed insights.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
