{"query": "AttendanceBot is not deducting sick time taken from sick time balances ", "retrieved_contexts": ["AttendanceBot Plans and Features", "AttendanceBot Plans and Features", "AttendanceBot Plans and Features"], "generated_answer": "If AttendanceBot is not deducting sick time from balances, follow these steps to troubleshoot:\n\n1. **Check Leave Type Configuration**: Ensure that the sick leave type is correctly configured with a balance and accrual rules.\n2. **Verify Employee Settings**: Confirm that the employee has been assigned the correct leave policy that includes sick leave.\n3. **Review Leave Requests**: Check if the sick leave requests are being approved and recorded properly.\n4. **Update AttendanceBot**: Make sure AttendanceBot is updated to the latest version to avoid any bugs.\n5. **Contact Support**: If the issue persists, consider reaching out to AttendanceBot support for further assistance.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000138965", "reference_answer": "If AttendanceBot is not deducting sick time from balances, check the leave type configuration, verify employee settings, review leave requests, ensure AttendanceBot is updated, and contact support if the issue persists.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
