{"query": "hi, i just have a question for customer service regarding our account. What is the best way to reach them", "retrieved_contexts": ["How can I get help from AttendanceBot support?", "How to change account admin", "Billing - how do I download past invoices or receipts?"], "generated_answer": "To reach AttendanceBot customer service, you have several options:\n\n1. Email support at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com or contact the support lead directly at sarah@harmonizehq.com.\n2. Raise a ticket by messaging 'dialm' as a direct message to AttendanceBot in Slack or Teams.\n3. Use the live chat feature by clicking the chat bubble on the AttendanceBot dashboard or website.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118263", "reference_answer": "To reach AttendanceBot customer service regarding your account, you can: 1. Email them at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com or contact the support lead directly at sarah@harmonizehq.com. 2. Raise a ticket by sending 'dialm' as a direct message to AttendanceBot in Slack or Teams. 3. Use the live chat feature on the AttendanceBot dashboard or website.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
