{"query": "I have a question on PTO tracking, can employees easily see their PTO accruals and balance?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to view employee status on a dashboard or in Slack", "Checking Your Leave Balance", "How to setup accrual rules and leave quotas based on company policy"], "generated_answer": "Yes, employees can easily check their PTO accruals and balance using AttendanceBot. Here's how:\n\n1. Type \"balance\" to the bot to view your leave balance, including details like \"Carry forwarded\", \"Days Taken\", \"Accrued\", and the \"Annual count\".\n2. If you're a manager, you can check the leave balance of your team members by typing \"balance @username\" to the bot.\n\nThis will display the leave balances and any leave types with unlimited balance will be shown at the end.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000116112", "reference_answer": "Employees can check their PTO accruals and balance by typing 'balance' to the AttendanceBot. Managers can check their team's balances using 'balance @username'. For more details, visit the AttendanceBot support page.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
