{"query": "why can the attendancebot modify channels?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to setup Slack channel notifications with AttendanceBot", "What can a manager do in AttendanceBot?", "AttendanceBot Plans and Features"], "generated_answer": "AttendanceBot can modify channels to provide real-time updates and notifications about team activities. This includes alerts for upcoming vacations, birthdays, work anniversaries, availability status, and shift changes. To enable these notifications, AttendanceBot needs to be added to the channel using the command \"/invite @attendancebot\". This allows it to make announcements and keep the team informed.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118249", "reference_answer": "AttendanceBot can modify channels to provide real-time updates and notifications about team activities, such as alerts for vacations and availability status. To enable these notifications, it needs to be invited to the channel using the command '/invite @attendancebot'.", "quality_score": 4.8, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "how to apply for backdated leave", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to apply for leave next year or any future year", "How can I apply for leave in Slack with AttendanceBot", "How to apply for recurring leave or hybrid status"], "generated_answer": "To apply for backdated leave in Slack using AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Direct message \"menu\" to AttendanceBot to open the options menu navigator.\n2. Click the \u2018Apply\u2019 button to open a request form popup.\n3. Complete your request by selecting the leave type, duration, and backdated date, then hit \u201cSubmit\u201d.\n\nNote: Ensure that your organization allows backdated leave requests, as this may vary based on company policy.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000131679", "reference_answer": "To apply for backdated leave in Slack using AttendanceBot, direct message 'menu' to AttendanceBot, click 'Apply', select the leave type, duration, and backdated date, then hit 'Submit'. Ensure your organization allows backdated leave requests.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
