{"query": "My team is having issues with receiving reminders/alerts to remind them to come back after lunch break", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to setup lunch hours for your team", "How to set up punch in/out reminders", "How to announce in/out and breaks/lunch on a Slack channel"], "generated_answer": "To set up reminders for your team to come back after lunch break, you can configure break notifications in AttendanceBot. Here's how:\n\n1. Ensure AttendanceBot is added to the relevant Slack channels.\n2. Navigate to \"Settings, people, policy\" > \"Notifications\" in the AttendanceBot menu.\n3. Click on \"Create new\" to configure a notification rule.\n4. Select \"Break/Lunch notifications,\" configure the channel, people, and timing for the notification, and save changes.\n\nThis will set up alerts for your team to remind them to return from lunch breaks.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000049835", "reference_answer": "To set up reminders for your team to come back after lunch break, you can configure break notifications in AttendanceBot. Ensure AttendanceBot is added to the relevant Slack channels, navigate to 'Settings, people, policy' > 'Notifications', click on 'Create new', select 'Break/Lunch notifications', configure the channel, people, and timing, and save changes.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
