{"query": "I need a timesheet report for the previous 3 weeks", "retrieved_contexts": ["How do I get the summary or report of my time in office?", "How to approve the timesheets of my reportees", "How to approve the timesheets of my reportees"], "generated_answer": "To get a timesheet report for the previous 3 weeks, follow these steps:\n\n1. Type the command \"Timesheet Report\" followed by the specific date range for the previous 3 weeks. For example, \"Timesheet Report Sep 1 to Sep 21\".\n2. You will receive a CSV report to download, which includes the timesheet data for the specified period.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118258", "reference_answer": "To get a timesheet report for the previous 3 weeks, type the command 'Timesheet Report' followed by the date range. For example, 'Timesheet Report [start date] to [end date]'. You will receive a CSV report to download. For more details, visit: https://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118258", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
