{"query": "how do i remove tiome off", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to configure and use time-off-in-lieu (TOIL) (Slack)", "How do I uninstall AttendanceBot from Google Chat ?", "How do I delete a leave applied by a member of my team?"], "generated_answer": "To delete a leave applied by a member of your team, follow these steps:\n\n1. Type the command \"delete @username\" to AttendanceBot, replacing \"@username\" with the team member's name.\n2. A list of approved leaves for that user will appear, both past and upcoming, with a Delete button below each leave.\n3. Click the Delete button for the leave you wish to remove. You will receive a notification confirming the deletion.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000116057", "reference_answer": "To delete a leave applied by a member of your team, type 'delete @username' to AttendanceBot, replacing '@username' with the team member's name. A list of approved leaves will appear, and you can click the Delete button for the leave you wish to remove. You will receive a notification confirming the deletion.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "how to remove vacation time ", "retrieved_contexts": ["Taking time off", "How to use and configure the AttendanceBot vacation calendar", "How to download team vacation data and reporting"], "generated_answer": "To remove or cancel vacation time in AttendanceBot, you typically need to follow these steps:\n\n1. Open your Slack and navigate to the AttendanceBot interface.\n2. Type a command or message to AttendanceBot indicating you want to cancel the vacation. For example, you might say \"cancel vacation\" or \"remove time off\".\n3. AttendanceBot will prompt you to confirm the cancellation. Follow the instructions to complete the process.\n\nIf you encounter any issues, consider opening a support ticket by typing 'ticket'.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000116053", "reference_answer": "To remove or cancel vacation time in AttendanceBot, you typically need to follow these steps: 1. Open your Slack and navigate to the AttendanceBot interface. 2. Type a command or message to AttendanceBot indicating you want to cancel the vacation, such as 'cancel vacation' or 'remove time off'. 3. Confirm the cancellation as prompted. For detailed instructions, visit: https://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000116053.", "quality_score": 4.8, "bucket": "well_answered"}
