{"query": "how to request for leaves?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to request hourly or half day leave", "How to apply for leave next year or any future year", "How to cancel / retract / rescind / delete a leave request"], "generated_answer": "To request a leave in AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Message \"menu\" to AttendanceBot to open the options menu navigator.\n2. Select \u2018Apply\u2019 to open a request form.\n3. Choose the leave type and specify the leave duration and dates.\n4. Hit \"Confirm\" to submit your leave request.\n\nFor hourly or half-day leaves, choose \u201cFew hours\u201d or \u201cfirst/second half\u201d under \u201cLeave Duration.\u201d Note that this option may not be available for all leave types, depending on your team's configuration.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000049824", "reference_answer": "To request a leave in AttendanceBot, follow these steps: 1. Message 'menu' to AttendanceBot to open the options menu navigator. 2. Select \u2018Apply\u2019 to open a request form. 3. Choose the leave type and specify the leave duration and dates. 4. Hit 'Confirm' to submit your leave request. For hourly or half-day leaves, choose 'Few hours' or 'first/second half' under 'Leave Duration.'", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
