{"query": "We have two employees that won't appear on the Personnel tab. Whenever I try to upload the list, it tells me that the employee does not exist. Please help us add them to our team.", "retrieved_contexts": ["How do I find my missing employee profile on the dashboard? (Slack)", "How do I assign managers for my employees?", "How to bulk update employee data using import / export functionality"], "generated_answer": "To resolve the issue of missing employee profiles on the dashboard, follow these steps:\n\n1. Go to the \"Settings\" panel and navigate to People > Personnel.\n2. Toggle off \"Show active personnel only\" to see all profiles.\n3. If you find their profile, ensure it's marked as \"active\" on the right.\n4. If you cannot find their profile, click the teal \"RE-SYNC\" button at the top.\n5. Wait 1-4 hours and then check again.\n\nIf the issue persists, consider opening a support ticket by typing 'ticket'.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000131680", "reference_answer": "To resolve the issue of missing employee profiles, go to Settings > People > Personnel, toggle off 'Show active personnel only', check if their profiles are active, and if not found, click 'RE-SYNC'. Wait 1-4 hours and check again. If the issue persists, open a support ticket.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
