{"query": "I would like to put in for a half day starting at 12:00 pm for an appointment, but everything I've tried doesn't work. ", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to request hourly or half day leave", "How to apply for time off for half a day or few hours?", "How to setup lunch hours for your team"], "generated_answer": "To apply for a half-day leave starting at 12:00 pm, follow these steps:\n\n1. Message \"menu\" to AttendanceBot to open the options menu navigator.\n2. Select \u2018Apply\u2019 to open a request form.\n3. Choose the leave type and under \u201cLeave Duration,\u201d select \u201csecond half.\u201d\n\nAlternatively, you can use a command directly by typing something like \"second half leave [date]\" and hit \"confirm.\"\n\nIf these options are not available, it might be due to your team's configuration. Contact your admin for assistance.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000049824", "reference_answer": "To apply for a half-day leave starting at 12:00 pm, message 'menu' to AttendanceBot, select 'Apply', choose the leave type, and select 'second half' under 'Leave Duration.' Alternatively, type 'second half leave [date]' and hit 'confirm.' If issues persist, contact your admin.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
