{"query": "where can I subscribe?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How do I change my credit card details?", "How long is my AttendanceBot trial?", "How to integrate calendars"], "generated_answer": "To subscribe to AttendanceBot, you need to follow these steps:\n\n1. Type \"settings\" as a direct message to the bot.\n2. Click on the settings dashboard link to open your Settings Panel.\n3. Navigate to the Settings--> Subscription page.\n4. Follow the instructions to subscribe to the app.\n\nIf you have more than 5 members, you will need to subscribe after the 14-day free trial. You can check the pricing plans here: https://www.attendancebot.com/pricing/\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000115577", "reference_answer": "To subscribe to AttendanceBot, type 'settings' in a direct message to the bot, access the settings dashboard, and navigate to the Subscription page. Follow the instructions provided there. If you have more than 5 members, you'll need to subscribe after the 14-day free trial. Check the pricing plans here: https://www.attendancebot.com/pricing/", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
