{"query": "How to delete a pending leave?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to cancel / retract / rescind / delete a leave request", "How do I delete a leave applied by a member of my team?", "How to delete approved leave for a reportee or employee"], "generated_answer": "To delete a pending leave request in AttendanceBot:\n\n1. Open the \"Menu\" and select \"Time off & hybrid work\".\n2. Look for the option to delete or rescind a requested leave, labeled \u201cDelete\u201d.\n3. This will display all approved or pending upcoming leaves.\n4. Click the \"Delete\" button below the leave details to cancel it. Both you and your manager will be notified.\n\nNote: If you need to delete a past leave, contact your manager or an admin.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000121203", "reference_answer": "To delete a pending leave request in AttendanceBot, open the 'Menu', select 'Time off & hybrid work', find the 'Delete' option, and click the 'Delete' button below the leave details. Both you and your manager will be notified. For past leaves, contact your manager or admin.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
