{"query": "How to export data", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to bulk update employee data using import / export functionality", "How to download team vacation data and reporting", "How can I generate reports?"], "generated_answer": "To export team data in AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Go to the \"People\" section on your AttendanceBot dashboard.\n2. Select \"Import Team Data.\"\n3. Download the current personnel data file.\n\nThis file can be edited and later re-uploaded to update employee information in bulk.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000124709", "reference_answer": "To export team data in AttendanceBot, go to the 'People' section on your dashboard, select 'Import Team Data,' and download the current personnel data file. This file can be edited and re-uploaded to update employee information in bulk.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
