{"query": "what is free plan", "retrieved_contexts": ["How long is my AttendanceBot trial?", "AttendanceBot Plans and Features", "AttendanceBot Plans and Features"], "generated_answer": "AttendanceBot offers a free plan for teams with 5 users or less. This plan includes a 14-day free trial for Slack and Microsoft Teams. After the trial, if your team has more than 5 members, you will need to subscribe to a paid plan. The app will not auto-charge your credit card after the trial period; you will be asked to subscribe explicitly.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000115577", "reference_answer": "AttendanceBot offers a free plan for teams with 5 users or less, including a 14-day free trial for Slack and Microsoft Teams. After the trial, teams with more than 5 members must subscribe to a paid plan, and there is no auto-charge after the trial period.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
