{"query": "I need help", "retrieved_contexts": ["How can I get help from AttendanceBot support?", "I'm getting an error message \"You are viewing the archives of a deactivated account\" while accessing AttendanceBot in Slack. What should I do?", "Getting Started, Action Menu Buttons, and Help Navigation"], "generated_answer": "To get help from AttendanceBot support, you can:\n\n1. Email support at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com or contact the support lead at sarah@harmonizehq.com.\n2. Raise a ticket by messaging 'dialm' directly to AttendanceBot in Slack.\n3. Use the chat bubble on the AttendanceBot dashboard or website for live support.\n4. Browse the article database on Freshdesk for self-help resources.\n\nIf you need further assistance, please let me know!\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118263", "reference_answer": "To get help from AttendanceBot support, you can email support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com, raise a ticket in Slack by messaging 'dialm', use the chat bubble on the dashboard, or browse the article database on Freshdesk.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
