{"query": "not with, I am asking about the communication with the representatives of your company", "retrieved_contexts": ["Billing - can I get a discount as a non-profit organization using AttendanceBot?", "How can I get help from AttendanceBot support?", " How to view overlapping leaves as an approving manager"], "generated_answer": "If you need to communicate with representatives of AttendanceBot, you can:\n\n1. Email support at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com.\n2. Directly email our support lead at sarah@harmonizehq.com.\n3. Message 'dialm' to AttendanceBot in Slack to open a ticket.\n4. Use the chat bubble on the AttendanceBot dashboard or website for live support.\n5. Email our founders at hi@harmonizehq.com for ideas and feedback.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118263", "reference_answer": "If you need to communicate with representatives of AttendanceBot, you can email support at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com, message 'dialm' in Slack, or use the chat bubble on the dashboard for live support.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
