{"query": "ho can i export timesheets", "retrieved_contexts": ["How do I get the summary or report of my time in office?", "How to approve the timesheets of my reportees", "How to approve the timesheets of my reportees"], "generated_answer": "To export timesheets, follow these steps:\n\n1. Type \"timesheet\" in Slack to get a summary of your current day's punch logs.\n2. For a report of your time in the office for the current and previous month, type \"timesheet report\" to receive a downloadable CSV report.\n3. To generate a report for a specific time period, append the date range to the report command, e.g., \"Timesheet Report jan 3 to feb 10\".\n4. Managers can type \"Report\", select the report type as Timesheet Report/Timesheet Summary Report, choose the relevant details, and hit \"Confirm\" to download a CSV report.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118258", "reference_answer": "To export timesheets, type 'timesheet' in Slack for a summary of your current day's punch logs. For a report of your time in the office for the current and previous month, type 'timesheet report' to receive a downloadable CSV report. To generate a report for a specific time period, append the date range to the report command, e.g., 'Timesheet Report jan 3 to feb 10'. Managers can type 'Report', select the report type as Timesheet Report/Timesheet Summary Report, choose the relevant details, and hit 'Confirm' to download a CSV report.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
