{"query": "how to delete 1 day of requested leave", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to cancel / retract / rescind / delete a leave request", "How to request hourly or half day leave", "How do I delete a leave applied by a member of my team?"], "generated_answer": "To delete a one-day leave request in AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Open the \"Menu\" in AttendanceBot and select \"Time off & hybrid work.\"\n2. You will see an option labeled \u201cDelete\u201d next to your requested leaves.\n3. Find the leave you want to delete and click the \u201cDelete\u201d button below the details.\n\nThis will immediately cancel the leave and notify both you and your manager. If the leave has already elapsed, you will need to ask your manager or an admin to delete it.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000121203", "reference_answer": "To delete a one-day leave request in AttendanceBot, open the 'Menu' and select 'Time off & hybrid work.' Click the 'Delete' button next to your requested leave. If the leave has already elapsed, contact your manager or admin for assistance.", "quality_score": 4.4, "bucket": "well_answered"}
