{"query": "where do I request my vacation", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to download team vacation data and reporting", "How to upload medical certificates for sick time", "How to apply for recurring leave or hybrid status"], "generated_answer": "To request a vacation, you can use AttendanceBot by typing a command in Slack. For example, you can type \"Vacation from [start_date] to [end_date]\" to request your leave. If you need more detailed instructions or have specific requirements, please let me know! \n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000049831", "reference_answer": "To request your vacation, follow these steps: 1. Type 'Apply' as a direct message (DM) to AttendanceBot. 2. Follow the prompt by entering details such as leave type, leave duration, and dates. 3. Hit 'Confirm' to submit your request. If you have any questions, you can open a ticket by typing 'Dial'.", "quality_score": 4.2, "bucket": "partial"}
