{"query": "how to define leave types", "retrieved_contexts": ["What are the different kinds of leaves?", "How to enable and understand leave privacy and hidden leave types", "How to setup accrual rules and leave quotas based on company policy"], "generated_answer": "To define leave types in AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Navigate to your settings dashboard by typing \"settings\" in Slack.\n2. Go to Vacation Management -> Leaves -> Leave Types and Quotas.\n3. Click \"Create New\" to define a new leave type.\n4. Title the leave and assign synonyms in the keywords section. These synonyms are words associated with the leave type and can be used when applying for leave.\n5. Save the new leave type.\n\nThis allows you to customize leave types according to your company's policies.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000051255", "reference_answer": "To define leave types in AttendanceBot, navigate to your settings dashboard, go to Vacation Management -> Leaves -> Leave Types and Quotas, and click 'Create New'. Title the leave, assign synonyms, and save the new leave type to customize according to your company's policies.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "how to define new leave types", "retrieved_contexts": ["What are the different kinds of leaves?", "How to setup accrual rules and leave quotas based on company policy", "How to setup accrual rules and leave quotas based on company policy"], "generated_answer": "To define new leave types in AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Navigate to the settings dashboard by typing \"settings\" in Slack.\n2. Go to Vacation Management --> Leaves --> Leave Types and Quotas.\n3. Click on \"Create New\" to define a new leave type.\n4. Title the leave and assign synonyms associated with it from the keywords section. These synonyms can be used while applying for leave.\n5. Configure additional settings like nomenclature, color coding, visibility, and privacy in the \"Basic Leave Settings\" tab.\n\nFor more detailed guidance, refer to the documentation.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000051255", "reference_answer": "To define new leave types in AttendanceBot, navigate to the settings dashboard, go to Vacation Management, and select Leave Types and Quotas. Click 'Create New', title the leave, assign synonyms, and configure additional settings in the Basic Leave Settings tab. For more details, refer to the documentation.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
