{"query": "where can i download the timesheet summary", "retrieved_contexts": ["How do I get the summary or report of my time in office?", "How to approve the timesheets of my reportees", "How to approve the timesheets of my reportees"], "generated_answer": "To download the timesheet summary, follow these steps:\n\n1. Type the command \"timesheet\" to get a summary for today.\n2. For a report of your time in office for the current and previous month, type \"timesheet report\" to receive a downloadable CSV report.\n3. To generate a report for a specific time period, append the date range to the report command, e.g., \"Timesheet Report jan 3 to feb 10\".\n\nManagers can type \"Report\" and select the report type as Timesheet Report/Timesheet Summary Report, then confirm to download the CSV report.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118258", "reference_answer": "To download the timesheet summary, type 'timesheet' for today's summary or 'timesheet report' for a downloadable CSV report of your time in office for the current and previous month. For a specific date range, use 'Timesheet Report [start date] to [end date]'. Managers can also select the report type in the system.", "quality_score": 4.8, "bucket": "well_answered"}
