{"query": "Turn on locations", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to set up offices and regional holiday calendars", "How to set up auto-punch out for my employees", "How to setup lunch hours for your team"], "generated_answer": "To turn on locations in AttendanceBot, follow these steps:\n\n1. Type 'settings' in the app to access the settings panel.\n2. Click on the \"Offices\" section in the sidebar navigation.\n3. Use the \"Create new\" option to create a new office location.\n4. Assign offices to employees by going to the \"People\" option in the sidebar and adding offices in their profile on the Personnel page.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000051706", "reference_answer": "To turn on locations in AttendanceBot, access the settings by typing 'settings' in the app. Navigate to the 'Offices' section and create a new office location. Assign offices to employees in their profiles under the 'People' option.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
