{"query": "I want to know how to apply for leave ", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to apply for leave next year or any future year", "How can I apply for leave in Slack with AttendanceBot", "How to apply leave on behalf of employee on Slack as admin/manager"], "generated_answer": "To apply for leave using AttendanceBot in Slack, follow these steps:\n\n1. Message \"menu\" to AttendanceBot to open the options menu navigator.\n2. Click the \u2018Apply\u2019 button to open a request form popup.\n3. Complete your request by choosing the leave type, duration, and date, then hit \u201cSubmit\u201d.\n\nYou can also shortcut the process by directly messaging AttendanceBot with the type and timing of the leave, like \u201csick today\u201d or \u201cpto next Thursday\u201d.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000131679", "reference_answer": "To apply for leave using AttendanceBot in Slack, type 'Apply' as a direct message to AttendanceBot. Follow the prompts to enter details like leave type, duration, and dates, then hit 'Confirm' to submit your application. You can also message AttendanceBot directly with your leave type and timing for a quicker process.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
