{"query": "contact customer support", "retrieved_contexts": ["How can I get help from AttendanceBot support?", "How to change account admin", "Billing - how do I download past invoices or receipts?"], "generated_answer": "To contact AttendanceBot customer support, you have several options:\n\n1. Email support at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com or the support lead at sarah@harmonizehq.com.\n2. Raise a ticket by messaging 'dialm' as a direct message to AttendanceBot in Slack or Teams.\n3. Use the live chat support by clicking the chat bubble on the AttendanceBot dashboard or website.\n4. Email the founders at hi@harmonizehq.com for ideas and feedback.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118263", "reference_answer": "To contact AttendanceBot customer support, you can email support at support@attendancebot.freshdesk.com, message 'dialm' in Slack or Teams to raise a ticket, use live chat on the AttendanceBot dashboard, or email the founders at hi@harmonizehq.com.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
