{"query": "How can I clock other users in", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to track time in Slack using AttendanceBot", "Time/Task tracking", "How to set up punch in/out reminders"], "generated_answer": "To clock other users in, you can use the AttendanceBot dashboard. Here\u2019s how:\n\n1. Go to the AttendanceBot dashboard.\n2. Navigate to \"Time Tracking.\"\n3. Select \"Edit Timesheet\" for the specific user.\n4. Use the command \"add punches @User\" and follow the prompts to clock them in.\n\nAlternatively, you can use the command \"edit punches @User\" to modify existing entries.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000115834", "reference_answer": "To clock other users in, go to the AttendanceBot dashboard, navigate to 'Time Tracking', select 'Edit Timesheet' for the user, and use 'add punches @User' to clock them in. You can also modify existing entries with 'edit punches @User'.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "where can i find an export of peoples attendance?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to bulk update employee data using import / export functionality", "How to download team vacation data and reporting", "How to upload medical certificates for sick time"], "generated_answer": "To export people's attendance data, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Open the \"Menu\" and select \"Data & Integrations\".\n2. Click on \"Reports\".\n3. Download the Leave Report for a history of all approved leaves, or choose the Leave Summary Report for total days/hours taken, or the Balance Report for current employee balances.\n4. Select the date range and choose to download data for all employees, a single employee, or a specific office or department.\n5. Confirm your selection to download the report.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000063984", "reference_answer": "To export people's attendance data, go to 'Menu' > 'Data & Integrations' > 'Reports'. Download the Leave Report, Leave Summary Report, or Balance Report by selecting the date range and employee criteria.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
