{"query": "is thre a way to add company holidays to OoO ?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to add a team holiday", "How to set up offices and regional holiday calendars", "How to configure overtime and time off in lieu (TOIL) rules?"], "generated_answer": "Yes, you can add company holidays to AttendanceBot. Follow these steps:\n\n1. Type \"settings\" as a direct message in Slack.\n2. Navigate to Vacation Management -> Calendar -> Holidays tab.\n3. Add your company holidays there.\n\nThis will allow your team to view upcoming holidays by typing 'holidays' in Slack.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118248", "reference_answer": "Yes, you can add company holidays to AttendanceBot. Type 'settings' in Slack, go to Vacation Management -> Calendar -> Holidays tab, and add your company holidays. Your team can view upcoming holidays by typing 'holidays' in Slack. For more details, refer to the article: https://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000118248.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
{"query": "Can holidays be displayed in the Outlook Calendar?", "retrieved_contexts": ["How to add a team holiday", "How to use and configure the AttendanceBot vacation calendar", "How to integrate your calendar with AttendanceBot for Slack"], "generated_answer": "Yes, you can display holidays in your Outlook Calendar by integrating it with AttendanceBot. Here's how:\n\n1. Start from the \"menu\" and select \"data & integrations\".\n2. Select \"Calendar\" on the sub-menu.\n3. Use the \"Get link\" button to copy an ICS calendar link.\n4. Sign in to Office365.\n5. Click on the \u201cOther Calendars\u201d menu, and choose \u201cOpen Calendar\u201d.\n6. Enter the URL into \u201cInternet Calendar\u201d and click \u201cOpen\u201d.\n\nThis will allow you to view your team's holidays and leave schedules in your Outlook Calendar.\n\nhttps://attendancebot.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/17000017361", "reference_answer": "Yes, you can display holidays in your Outlook Calendar by integrating it with AttendanceBot. Follow the steps to copy the ICS calendar link and add it to your Outlook Calendar.", "quality_score": 5.0, "bucket": "well_answered"}
